snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard | Who's Telling the Truth In Court ?
snippet.description:
In this video we are going to talk about Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard in Court and what both sides are saying. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

While Johnny Depp is no stranger to the courtroom - having been involved in several different lawsuits in recent years - none have been as impactful or bitter as his ongoing feud with ex-wife Amber Heard.  Did Johnny Depp abuse Amber Heard, both physically and psychologically?  Or were the allegations faked by Amber Heard, as Johnny Depp and his legal team still contend?
